OL,3,CSister of murdered woman says hospital
OL,4,Corder is 'meaningless sentence'
OL,6,FAnabah was diagnosed as having
OL,7,Fparanoid schizophrenia and admitted
OL,8,Ftwo counts of manslaughter with
OL,9,Fdiminished responsibility.
OL,11,FThe family were told he would be held
OL,12,Findefinitely in a secure hospital.
OL,14,FBut two years later, Yemi received an
OL,15,Femail "out of the blue" saying Anabah
OL,16,Fwas going to the Mental Health
OL,17,FTribunal and he could be discharged.
OL,18,FAfter which she began "shaking and
OL,19,Fcrying".
