OL,3,CSister of murdered woman says hospital
OL,4,Corder is 'meaningless sentence'
OL,6,FYemi said the family was also not told
OL,7,Fwhen the offender was allowed escorted
OL,8,Fvisits into the community.
OL,10,FShe told ITV News London: "This is our
OL,11,FMr Bates vs The Post Office, in terms
OL,12,Fof families who are being short-
OL,13,Fchanged by the CPS, selling us this
OL,14,Fmeaningless sentencing."
OL,16,FBut at the eleventh hour, just like
OL,17,Fthe families in Nottingham, instead of
OL,18,Fmurder, the killer would plead guilty
OL,19,Fto two counts of manslaughter - citing
OL,20,Fhis diagnosis of paranoid
OL,21,Fschizophrenia.
