OL,3,CSister of murdered woman says hospital
OL,4,Corder is 'meaningless sentence'
OL,6,FShe is calling for a tariff or a
OL,7,Fminimum term attached to indefinite
OL,8,Fhospital orders.
OL,10,FYemi also wants a section 45A to be
OL,11,Fapplied, which means offenders who
OL,12,Fsuffer from a treatable mental
OL,13,Fcondition are returned to the criminal
OL,14,Fsystem to serve out the remainder of
OL,15,Ftheir sentences once they are well.
OL,17,FMost importantly, Yemi wants an end to
OL,18,Fannual reviews which gives hospital
OL,19,Forder offenders the right to have
OL,20,Ftheir sentences assessed after just
OL,21,Fsix months.
