OL,3,CSister of murdered woman says hospital
OL,4,Corder is 'meaningless sentence'
OL,6,FShe said: "This is his automatic
OL,7,Fright, their automatic right every
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,F"Every year they are entitled to this
OL,11,F- it's automatic, what the guidance
OL,12,Fsays."
OL,14,FSpeaking about the impact on her and
OL,15,Fher family, she said: "It is torture
OL,16,Ffor me. Last year I had three
OL,17,Fnotifications in one year.
OL,19,F"This is the honest truth, three
OL,20,Fnotifications in one year."
